			Volume
			A Volume control Applet
			And a Mixer for ROX
			by Ken Hayber

Brief
~~~~~
No, really.  It is a Volume control applet and a Mixer for ROX.
Written in python/pygtk (what else?) and supporting OSS (or Alsa-OSS emulation)


