Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~
ROX 2.1.0 or higher
ROX-Lib2 1.9.13 or higher
Pygtk 1.9.18 or better?
Python 2.3 or better


Instructions
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Drag the AppIcon to the Panel to run as an applet.
Left click to show the volume slider.
Middle-click/drag to position it.
Right click for Options (mixer device, PCM or Master volume control).

Supports Bottom, Top, Left, Right panels.

Run as a normal AppDir to use as a Mixer.  Supports stereo and mono controls.  Discovers
your controls automatically (via ossaudiodev)

Email the author for help :)
	khayber(a)socal.rr.com
